     <h2><a href="http://greshams-law.com/2011/07/12/panic-is-in-the-air/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Panic is in the Air&#8230;">Panic is in the Air&#8230;</a></h2>
     <div class="date">Jul 12, 2011</div>
      </div>
    <div class="clearer"></div>
    <p>Well, seemingly markets are in &#8216;risk-off&#8217; mode again, with everything but the dollar, yen and government debt taking a hit. I thought I&#8217;d point out <a title="Some Thoughts on the Dollar &amp; the Weekly Federal Reserve Balance Sheet Charts" href="http://greshams-law.com/2011/06/24/some-thoughts-on-the-dollar-the-weekly-federal-reserve-balance-sheet-charts/">our opinion on the dollar</a> in case anyone missed it the other week.</p>
