     <h2><a href="http://greshams-law.com/2011/07/09/weekly-fed-balance-sheet-update-thoughts-on-shorter-term-movements/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Weekly Fed Balance Sheet Update &amp; Thoughts on Shorter-term Movements.">Weekly Fed Balance Sheet Update &#038; Thoughts on Shorter-term Movements.</a></h2>
     <div class="date">Jul 9, 2011</div>
      </div>
    <div class="clearer"></div>
    <div class="sticky_post"><p>An update of the weekly Federal Reserve balance sheet charts for 9/7/11. As the latest quantitative easing program was completed on June 30th, this will be the last week where the numbers coming from the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System reflect it. [The latest data point reflects the changes from 29th June to 6th July.]</p>
